{"tid":1385291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌塞地鐵果班人 我屌晒你地老母！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:40:58.000Z","uid":266138,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7f0ca991af9850a280c5f0d5ac56e773e4853e","tid":1385291,"uid":266138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"6月到而家 你付出過啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n遊行有冇去、集會有冇去、捐錢捐物資有冇、接仔放學落街屌黑警有冇、罷工有冇、全民黑衫有冇？<br />\n<br />\n叫你地罷工又驚炒、而家人地幫晒你、俾晒機會你地罷工、轉個頭又屌鳩人、又話咩民意乜乜乜、屌你啦 兩個月都黎啦 係藍係黃一早企好晒啦<br />\n<br />\n仲撚好笑係又話暈又話焗、你唔撚諗下班義士30幾度帶撚晒口罩企係街到曬？仲要係咁食彈、隨時命都冇撚埋呀、你焗果一陣算啲乜撚野？<br />\n<br />\n真係咁撚鍾意番工嘅、早啲出門口搭頭班咪唔會塞囉屌你<br />\n<br />\n一係你就拎個更好嘅建議出黎、否則全力支持前線決定！！！"},{"pid":"08bead3c16bc4d759b7641d8e97aac88ee3c8012","tid":1385291,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c89f2f88770a745c22602c198a8819211f1dd03","tid":1385291,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同黑犬攻防戰必須遵守既一項基本原則<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385238</a>"},{"pid":"bbf62d892d29655f1504a71669c4bda10c14d8af","tid":1385291,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"8d36eb600f1f0e1a10ef6307f7b1b6b45a16338b","tid":1385291,"uid":22288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d70adc11864307098d00dfb82cf5cff6a77fde4","tid":1385291,"